APP ATTACH
Dynamically attaches applications to user session in AVD
Apps not installed locally on session host
Reduces image management overhead & cost
Apps run inside containers for isolation/security

BENEFITS OF APP ATTACH

Apps delivered as RemoteApp/Desktop
Per-user app permissions
Same package usable across multiple host pools
Apps can run on any session host in same Azure region
Easy upgrades without maintenance window
Multiple app versions supported simultaneously

SUPPORTED PACKAGE TYPES

MSIX → .msix / .msixbundle
APPX → .appx / .appxbundle
App-V

MSIX APP ATTACH
